lead_paragraph: Australian Open champion Angelique Kerber made a disappointing return to tournament tennis on Tuesday, losing 7-5, 6-1 to China's Zheng Saisai in the second round at the Qatar Open.

headline.print_headline: Kerber Loses in 1st Match at Qatar Open
